                    <h4 class="service-heading"><a href="civics.html"><i>Civics and Citizenship</i></a></h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Our after-school civic engagement program, <i>Civics and Citizenship</i> helps immigrant youth to become active participants in the civic life of their communities and pursue the many opportunities available. Participants engage in the civic life of their community by taking visits to local civic institutions such as police and fire stations or courthouses, and participate in volunteerism. Youth learn about different higher education and career opportunities by taking field trips to institutions of higher education and meeting working professionals in different fields (often of immigrant background themselves), and much more.</p>
