                    <h4 class="service-heading"><a href="cebell.html"><i> Civic Engagement for Beginning English language Learners (CE-BELL) </i></a></h4>
                    <p class="text-muted"><i>CE-BELL</i> follows the format of <i>Civics and Citizenship</i>, but focuses on <strong>youth who have no or very limited English language skills</strong>, and includes an English language learning component. The program, <strong>delivered entirely in Spanish</strong>, exposes newly arrived Hispanic immigrants to the civic life of their communities and encourages them to get involved early on. Like <i>Civics and Citizenship</i>, participants also learn about higher education and career opportunities.</p>
